drm/msm/dpu: simplify DPU_SSPP features checks

Add DPU_SSPP_CSC_ANY denoting any CSC block. As we are at it, rewrite
DPU_SSPP_SCALER (any scaler) to use BIT(x) instead of hand-coded
bitshifts.

